{"tid":2391511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律政司引23條：非犯法行為危害國安","createTime":"2021-02-02T09:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T10:48:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f1ff4f26b0a8792e16a0b8c5dc766e8dc4af09","tid":2391511,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/NFU4SBG6CJDDXNVRHCXG6GK7HQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FNFU4SBG6CJDDXNVRHCXG6GK7HQ%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=e9f21e58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FNFU4SBG6CJDDXNVRHCXG6GK7HQ%2F&h=41993a49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/NFU4SBG6CJDDXNVRHCXG6GK7HQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n律政司引23條：非犯法行為危害國安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4rf15wxJWhpVRDmCKSRmo9kgPW0=/818x543/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WW6QR3ZMXJALHCE7TD77YGNECM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4rf15wxJWhpVRDmCKSRmo9kgPW0%3D%2F818x543%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWW6QR3ZMXJALHCE7TD77YGNECM.jpg&h=424d8c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周天行<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國安法第42條提及危害國家安全的行為，律政司昨就「行為。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「軟禁難防再犯案 」終院質疑  黎智英還柙候判<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張舉能：邏輯奇怪<br />\n<br />\n批准黎智英保釋的高院法。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n非常任法官陳兆愷要求舉例，周以《基本法》第23條為例，指外國政治組織或團體在本港進行政治活動，或本港政治組織或團體與外國政治組織或團體建立聯繫亦包括在內，但周不諱言23條尚未立法。陳官即質疑：「即不是罪行？為何要關注？」<br />\n<br />\n常任法官李義接着表示，難理解若法庭考慮不是罪行的行為，如何幫助保障國安，明言「想不到有甚麼行為是危害國安，但不違法」，亦要求周舉例。周回應指，例如一些已構成危害國安的犯罪行為（actus reus），但因撇除犯罪意圖，故未構成完整罪行。首席法官張舉能則謂，據律政司邏輯，「市民可自由地作出一些違反國安的行為，不會被拘捕；但國安法被告卻因這些其他人可自由作出的行為，而須被羈押？」直言：「難道這不是頗為奇怪？」卜。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"2cb753c4ee71846ff92b882a1ea155d48785bb27","tid":2391511,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"即係要殺人放火就唔犯国安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4b681cfea109bd1904669d038ddd658c8e49f8","tid":2391511,"uid":8776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cb753c4ee71846ff92b882a1ea155d48785bb27","tid":2391511,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"即係要殺人放火就唔犯国安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"咁就要睇你殺咩人同燒邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有高尚同暴徒之分"},{"pid":"28d8f2a762596e32a1275f2c242b628bd029b2fa","tid":2391511,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"Department of joke 真係9up唔洗本<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b60ea64c6ac650487247a4cd13bed63fe35b17","tid":2391511,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"「軟禁難防再犯案」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 監禁又可以阻止犯案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b618d0ac1e04094b17be938a4f75a5adc90fb6","tid":2391511,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"黑警+律政狗=曱甴集團"},{"pid":"a012b5beab54774749ed64f210b46b72f24a52df","tid":2391511,"uid":296450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"一但被控國安法, 日常行為例如食飯痾屎都會觸犯國安法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}